# Impeccable + ChamiNext

Before editing UI in this project:

1. Read [PRODUCT.md](../../PRODUCT.md) and [DESIGN.md](../../DESIGN.md) at repo root.
2. For design/redesign/polish tasks, follow the Impeccable skill (`~/.cursor/skills/impeccable` or `~/Desktop/impeccable/.cursor/skills/impeccable`).
3. Product surfaces: Practice, Daily, Interview Simulator, Ship Tests, Profile, Employers.
4. Brand surfaces: HomePage, Pricing.

Avoid: hero-metric clichés, identical card grids, gradient text everywhere, decorative glass on every element, side-stripe borders, em dashes in copy.

Match existing tokens in `src/styles/design-system.css`; prefer CSS variables over new one-off colors.
